10 An Act relating to the Teachers’ Retirement System of
Oklahoma; amending 3A O.S. 2021, Section 713, as last
11 amended by Section 5, Chapter 443, O.S.L. 2024 (3A
O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 713), which relates to the
12 apportionment of Oklahoma lottery proceeds; ceasing
certain apportionment to the Teachers’ Retirement
13 System Dedicated Revenue Revolving Fund upon certain
conditions; increasing certain apportionment under
14 certain conditions; amending 62 O.S. 2021, Section
3103, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 361,
15 O.S.L. 2024 (62 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 3103), which
relates to the Oklahoma Pension Legislation Actuarial
16 Analysis Act; modifying certain definition; amending
68 O.S. 2021, Sections 1353, as last amended by
17 Section 4, Chapter 441, O.S.L. 2024, 1403, and 2352
(68 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 1353), which relate to
18 the apportionment of tax proceeds; ceasing certain
apportionment to certain fund upon certain
19 conditions; increasing certain apportionment under
certain conditions; authorizing benefit increase for
20 certain retired members of the Teachers’ Retirement
System of Oklahoma; updating statutory language;
21 providing for codification; and providing effective
dates.
22
23
24 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
